 * Sell within 21 days : %20 (%10 marketing, %5 burn, %5 RFI) = Slippage Min: 25
 * Sell within 30 days : %10 (%7 marketing, %1 burn, %2 RFI) = Slippage Min: 11
 * sell after 30 days  : %5  (%4 marketing, %0.5 burn, %0.5 RFI) = Slippage Min: 6
